It's the the year 2323, and nothing's left that's free (Apologies to Zagar and Evans).
Anyway, all of human civilisation has been enslaved throughout the galaxy by an all-mighty Software Corporation named 'MegaSoft'.
It all began back in 2207, when the military and police forces were automated, because it was cheaper to maintain. The technology extended to interstellar traffic monitoring... even in space, they were there in their nasty uniforms and clipboards.
By 2313, almost all the droids were running a MegaSoft operating system.
By the dawn of 2320, it turned out that this proprietary OS was a trojan horse and from then on only responded to MS instruction signals.
It soon became realised that military and police forces were under MS control.  
Interstellar traffic now depends upon MS allowance.
Droids are roaming the streets and announcing the new rule.
Any resistance is met with utter violence.

But some 20 years after the MS took over the government, the droids running the MS operating system suddenly went bonkers and attacked all life forms, MS and non-MS alike.  
Few survived this day, that is known as the 'Great Assault' in todays history.
The few survivers formed small colonies in the outskirts of the galaxy.
There they live underground, struggling to survive...

But that was in the past... and we are at the present.

